294
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:17,600
They're just trying to scare us.

295
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,360
Anyway, I trust Officer Jiang.

296
00:16:19,639 --> 00:16:20,679
He's the one who saved us.

297
00:16:23,559 --> 00:16:24,240
Officer,

298
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:25,960
I trust you too.

299
00:16:26,159 --> 00:16:27,360
We both trust you.

300
00:16:27,759 --> 00:16:29,639
But can you trust me, just this once?

301
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:30,960
I just had surgery.

302
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:31,840
It really hurts.

303
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,320
Can we talk another day?

304
00:16:34,279 --> 00:16:34,919
Fine.

305
00:16:35,639 --> 00:16:36,879
Since you don't trust us,

306
00:16:37,519 --> 00:16:38,200
I won't force it.

307
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:42,320
But there's one thing I must tell you.

308
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:44,240
Once the two of us walk out that door,

309
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,320
all police protection will be withdrawn.

310
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,399
You should know the consequences.

311
00:16:47,159 --> 00:16:49,080
You know exactly who you've crossed.

312
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:50,840
You don't care about your own life,

313
00:16:51,159 --> 00:16:52,399
but don't you care about Xiao Hong's?

314
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:54,799
Are you trying to scare me?

315
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:56,200
Me, scare you?

316
00:16:56,639 --> 00:16:57,840
Xiao Hong, pull up your shirt for him.

317
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:58,639
What for?

318
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:05,319
Last night,

319
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,759
if I hadn't gotten there in time,

320
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:08,279
you'd both be dead.

321
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:10,039
The moment you step out of this hospital,

322
00:17:10,279 --> 00:17:11,519
and lose police protection,

323
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:13,480
they'll kill you in an instant.

324
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,240
Enough.

325
00:17:14,839 --> 00:17:15,720
It's their lives.

326
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:17,279
Won't force it. Let's go.

327
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:19,839
Brother Hu, please, tell the truth.

328
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:22,240
I really don't want to go through last night again.

329
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,000
I have one condition.

330
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:25,359
You guys

331
00:17:26,359 --> 00:17:27,480
have to keep us safe.
